snippet.title: JanKenUp! How far can you go up?
snippet.description:
GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.humita.jankenup
AppStore: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/jankenup/id1562022513
UpToDown: https://com-humita-jankenup.en.uptodown.com/android
QooApp: https://apps.qoo-app.com/en/app/17257

✊ Play rock, paper, and scissors while riding an elevator with no maximum floor.
🖐 Single player: unlock all characters, beat your records and get all the available achievements.
✌ Online Mode: Become the best player in the world or beat your friends in private tournaments.
